Implement BonsaiConfig parsed from bonsai.toml: [reduce] (roots, test), [reduce.dependencies] (paths, exclude). discover(start_path): walk up parents looking for bonsai.toml, stop at filesystem root. load(path): parse toml. CLI flag merging: --roots, --deps, --exclude-deps, --config override config. DependencyConfig from merged config. Precedence: CLI > config > defaults. See multi-file spec "Configuration File" and call-inlining spec "Configuration".
